@startuml Sequence_UC02
title UC-02: Kelola Kategori Produk

actor "Bagian Inventori" as User
participant "Halaman Kategori\n(livewire/category)" as View
participant "Category\\Index\n(Livewire)" as Component
participant "Category Model" as CategoryModel
database "Database" as DB

User -> View: Membuka /kategori
View -> Component: mount()
Component -> DB: SELECT categories ORDER BY name
DB --> Component: Collection<Category>
Component --> View: Render daftar kategori

== Tambah Kategori ==
User -> View: Mengisi nama kategori\nlalu klik Simpan
View -> Component: save()
Component -> Component: validate(['name' => 'required|min:3|unique'])
alt Validasi gagal
  Component --> View: Tampilkan pesan kesalahan
  View --> User: Pesan validasi
else Validasi berhasil
  Component -> CategoryModel: Category::create(['name' => $name])
  CategoryModel -> DB: INSERT INTO categories
  DB --> CategoryModel: Category baru
  Component --> View: Tampilkan notifikasi sukses & list terbaru
end

== Ubah Kategori ==
User -> View: Klik ikon edit, ubah nama, lalu simpan
View -> Component: edit($id), save()
Component -> CategoryModel: Category::findOrFail($id)->update(...)
CategoryModel -> DB: UPDATE categories SET name = ? WHERE id = ?
Component --> View: Notifikasi sukses

== Hapus Kategori ==
User -> View: Klik hapus pada kategori
View -> Component: delete($id)
Component -> CategoryModel: Category::findOrFail($id)->delete()
CategoryModel -> DB: DELETE FROM categories WHERE id = ?
Component --> View: Notifikasi sukses & list diperbarui

@enduml
